{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"447ba0e1-9e64-4659-9048-c5b4dcb19bd9","content":"Yes, you'll hit **framework compatibility issues**. MSTest v3 dropped support for end-of-life runtimes. Looking at your targets:\n\n| Target | MSTest v3 Support |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ Dropped (EOL) |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ Dropped (EOL) |\n\n**Two of your three targets are unsupported.** You'd need to update them to supported versions (e.g., `net6.0` or `net8.0`).\n\nOther migration notes:\n- **Package consolidation**: MSTest v3 replaces the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages with a single `MSTest` meta-package.\n- **Breaking API changes**: Some v2 APIs were removed or changed in v3, so review your test code against the migration guide.\n\nIf you can't drop `netcoreapp3.1`/`net5.0`, you'll need to stay on MSTest v2.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0f64d062-f931-411f-b274-28137ae4e2cc","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Let me analyze the project:\n\n1. **Target frameworks**: `net5.0`, `net462`, `netcoreapp3.1`\n2. **MSTest version**: 2.2.10 (TestFramework + TestAdapter)\n3. **Test SDK**: 17.5.0\n\nMSTest v3 has important compatibility changes:\n\n1. **Dropped framework support**: MSTest v3 dropped support for older TFMs. Specifically:\n   - `.NET 5.0` is no longer supported (it's end-of-life)\n   - `netcoreapp3.1` is no longer supported (it's end-of-life)\n   - `.NET Framework 4.6.2` may also be unsupported — I'm seeing conflicting information about whether v3 requires 4.7.2 or supports 4.6.2 and later\n   - `.NET Core 3.1` and `.NET 5.0` are definitely out of support, so MSTest v3 dropped them\n   - The user will face compatibility issues with `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1`, while `net462` should work if the minimum is indeed 4.6.2\n\n+\n   - Beyond the TFM changes, MSTest v3 also introduced breaking changes to APIs and consolidated the package structure into a single `MSTest` package","outputTokens":831,"requestId":"63C3:239FAB:446A612:4A8F09D:6A02FAE0"},"id":"ceda89c3-d55e-4a6f-817f-e913ea25a459","timestamp":"2026-05-12T10:03:33.675Z","parentId":"68b3f4ea-89f9-4d58-92bd-3304b9559f01"}
